name: SAVE THE DATES - Printable Custom Digital - Eco Bicycle Theme
description:
{Download, Print, Send!}

Sweet, simple and modern eco bicycle themed Save the Date. We suggest printing on Kraft recycled paper with vegetable soy ink.

This listing includes a printable digital file in PDF or JPEG format. You will have unlimited access to your digital file.

This listing is for one Save the Date flat card at either 4x6 or 5x7 inches 
(or custom size upon request).

Print as many copies as you want at your local printing place or ask us for our list of recommended online printers.

.......................................................................................................................................

{Customization}

In the section, "Message to Seller," please include the following:

1) Couple's Names
2) Wedding Date
3) City & Town
5) Colors

.......................................................................................................................................

{How It Works}

1. Purchase the design for the listed price
2. Send us the customization details
3. You will receive a jpeg to proof in 24-48 hours
4. Send us your changes and we will revise the proof until you are completely happy
5. You receive the final high-quality digital file to print at home (alternatively, we can recommend an online printing source)

* Please note only the coloring and the wording are editable and the design is locked and copyrighted.

* Please note that the 'Five Sparrows' logo watermark will be removed on final print.

***All designs and templates for personal use only. 
Copyright Five Sparrows Design***

.......................................................................................................................................

Custom Orders available!
